<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="332" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,151,680]" pageId="16" pageNumber="332">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,335,548,573]" pageId="16" pageNumber="332">Comments.</emphasis>
This species is distinguished by its pale yellow legs with darker yellow femur, the smooth head, mesosoma with granulate sculpturing and the metasoma sculpturing pattern.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
